'''Advanced Recon Commando heavy gunners (ARC heavy gunners)''' were the vanguards of the [[Advanced Recon Commando/Legends|Advanced Recon Commandos]], making use of powerful heavy weapons.

==Description==
[[File:ARC-PLX1_BF.jpg|thumb|left|150px|An ARC trooper with a [[PLX-1/Legends|PLX-1 portable missile launcher]].]]
Wielding high-powered rapid-firing weapons such as the [[Reciprocating quad blaster cannon/Legends|reciprocating quad blaster]] or the [[Z-6 rotary blaster cannon/Legends|Z-6 rotary blaster cannon]],<ref name="CW21">{{CW|21}}</ref> they were the scourge of [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] vehicles. Their specialized armor was equipped with a direct feed from their helmets' HUDs to their heavy weapons, granting them extra targeting capability.<ref name="DB">{{DB|technology|cipquad|Reciprocating Quad Blaster (Cip-Quad)}}</ref> Other ARC heavy gunners were equipped with [[PLX-1/Legends|PLX-1 portable missile launchers]], [[DC-15S/Legends|DC-15S]], [[V-1 thermal detonator]]s, and [[HX2 antipersonnel mine]]s.<ref name="BF">''[[Star Wars: Battlefront]]''</ref>

==History==
During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], ARC [[heavy weapon specialist]]s fought on [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]], [[First Battle of Kamino|Kamino]], [[Battle of Rhen Var (Clone Wars)|Rhen Var]], and [[Battle of Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]].<ref name="BF" />

[[File:ARCHeavyGunners.jpg|thumb|right|180px|Two ARC heavy gunners during the [[Battle of Hypori/Legends|Battle of Hypori]].]]
A team of gunners assisted the ARC trooper squad during the rescue mission of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] strike force during the [[Battle of Hypori/Legends|Battle of Hypori]].<ref name="CW21" />

===Rail ARC troopers===
A variation of the ARC heavy gunners were the [[Rail-class Advanced Recon Commando]]s. They also wielded Z-6 rotary cannons and were one of the trooper types found among the [[anti-trooper]]s after the [[Declaration of a New Order]]. Anti-troopers [[Kamino uprising|fought]] [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] as well as [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]].<ref name="BFII">''[[Star Wars: Battlefront II]]''</ref>

